        <title>Code Reviews with Gerrit</title>
        <paragraph>Manila uses the <reference name="Gerrit" refuri="http://code.google.com/p/gerrit">Gerrit</reference> tool to review proposed code changes. The review site
            is <reference refuri="http://review.openstack.org">http://review.openstack.org</reference>.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Gerrit is a complete replacement for Github pull requests. <title_reference>All Github pull
                requests to the manila repository will be ignored</title_reference>.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>See the <reference name="Development Workflow" refuri="http://docs.openstack.org/infra/manual/developers.html#development-workflow">Development Workflow</reference> for more detailed documentation on how
            to work with Gerrit.</paragraph>
